[246.81866, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mReconnect semantics\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BRe-attach = devic\u001b[22Gkey + session id\u001b[39G+ last-s\u001b[48Gen \u001b[52Gequence number per stream.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BClyffy replays the\u001b[23Gutbox\u001b[29Gfrom\u001b[34Gthat seq; client-side\u001b[56Gingestion resumes from\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe last j\u001b[14Gurna\u001b[19Ged offset with idemp\u001b[41Gen\u001b[44G frame\u001b[51Gkeys (\u001b[58Guplicates from the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bretry window collapse). No \"sync negotiation\"\u001b[49G—\u001b[51Gthe\u001b[55Gledger\u001b[62Gis\u001b[65Gthe\u001b[69Gtruth,\u001b[76Gthe\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bclient\u001b[10Gjust\u001b[15Gsays\u001b[20Gwhere\u001b[26Git\u001b[29Ggot\u001b[33Gto.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mThe two questions only you can answer\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B1. \u001b[1mSession ⇄ device cardinality.\u001b[22m One session bound\u001b[54Gto one device is simplest.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BBut do y\u001b[12Gu\u001b[14Gwant the estate\u001b[30Gm\u001b[32Gve\u001b[35G— \u001b[40G s\u001b[43Gme session attachable from\u001b[70Gthe\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdev\u001b[7Gtation \u001b[3mand\u001b[23m the Windo\u001b[56Ge live atta\u001b[69G at\u001b[73Ga time)\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
