[257.188615, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mReconnect semantics\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BRe-attach\u001b[13G=\u001b[15Gdevice\u001b[22Gkey\u001b[26G+\u001b[28Gsession\u001b[36Gid\u001b[39G+\u001b[41Glast-seen\u001b[51Gsequence\u001b[60Gnumber\u001b[67Gper\u001b[71Gstream.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BClyffy replays th\u001b[22Goutbox from that\u001b[39Gseq; cli\u001b[48Gnt-\u001b[52Gide ingestion resumes from\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe last journaled\u001b[23Gffset\u001b[29Gwith\u001b[34Gidempotent frame keys\u001b[56G(duplicates from the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bretry wind\u001b[14Gw co\u001b[19Glapse). No \"sync neg\u001b[41Gia\u001b[44Gion\" —\u001b[51Gthe le\u001b[58Gger is the truth, the\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bclient just says where it got to.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mThe two questions only you can answer\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B1.\u001b[6G\u001b[1mSession ⇄ device cardinality.\u001b[36G\u001b[22mOne\u001b[40Gsession\u001b[48Gbound\u001b[54Gto\u001b[57Gone\u001b[61Gdevice\u001b[68Gis\u001b[71Gsimplest.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BBut do you want the estate move — the same session\u001b[54Gattachable from the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdevstati\u001b[12Gn\u001b[14G\u001b[3mand\u001b[23m the Windows\u001b[30Gb\u001b[32Gx,\u001b[35Gei\u001b[40Gr \u001b[43Gs handoff (one live attach\u001b[70Gat a\u001b[75Gtime)\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bor \u001b[7Gpectate (read-only s\u001b[56Ghe ledger s\u001b[69Gema\u001b[73Gnow,\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
