[347.481237, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[1B\u001b[48;5;237m\u001b[38;5;239m❯ \u001b[38;5;231mi think it should be i guess for now session bound one device but can we have\u001b[39m \r\u001b[1B  \u001b[4G\u001b[38;5;231mt evolve int\u001b[17G estate mov\u001b[30G,\u001b[32Gand\u001b[36Gdispatches where we prefl\u001b[62Gght and conn\u001b[75Gct \u001b[39m  \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231mqr\u001b[6Gcode sca\u001b[15G we can deploy vi\u001b[33G phone\u001b[39m                                       \r\u001b[1B\u001b[49m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mThat\u001b[8Gevolves\u001b[16Gcleanly\u001b[24G—\u001b[26Gand\u001b[30Git\u001b[33Gtells\u001b[39Gme\u001b[42Gthe\u001b[46Gschema\u001b[53Gdecision:\u001b[63G\u001b[1mattachment becomes\r\u001b[1B\u001b[22m \u001b[3G\u001b[1ma first-class entity from day one\u001b[22m, ev\u001b[41Gn thoug\u001b[49G v1\u001b[53Gpol\u001b[57Gcy enforces exactly one\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Blive attach. Concretely:\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5G\u001b[38;5;153msession\u001b[13G\u001b[39m←→\u001b[16G\u001b[38;5;153mattachment\u001b[27G\u001b[39m←→\u001b[30G\u001b[38;5;153mdevice\u001b[37G\u001b[39min\u001b[40Gthe\u001b[44Gconnectome\u001b[55Gschema.\u001b[63GV1\u001b[66Gships\u001b[72Gwith\u001b[77Ga\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bpolicy knob (\u001b[38;5;153mmax_liv\u001b[24G_attachments = 1\u001b[39m), not a hardcoded assumption. Estate\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bm\u001b[5Gves and phone dispatch then become \u001b[3mpolicy and ceremony changes, not schema \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bmigrations\u001b[23m — which is exactly\u001b[33Gthe trap we're avoiding by deciding this now.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mAttachment gets a \u001b[38;5;153mrole\u001b[39m field\u001b[22m now: \u001b[38;5;153mprimary\u001b[39m (full data plane — the\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdevstation), \u001b[38;5;153mdispatcher\u001b[39m (control-plane only\u001b[47G— what the\u001b[59Gho\u001b[64Gis), \u001b[38;5;153mspectator\u001b[39m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
