[353.083657, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Gdevstation), \u001b[38;5;153mdispatcher\u001b[39m (control-plane only\u001b[47G— what the\u001b[59Gho\u001b[64Gis), \u001b[38;5;153mspectator\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m(read-only, reserved). A phone disp\u001b[39Gtch \u001b[44Gever\u001b[49Gneeds the QUIC\u001b[64Gfast\u001b[69Gpath; it\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bne\u001b[6Gds the HTTP/3 control\u001b[29Gla\u001b[34Gto \u001b[38Greflight and fire. So \"deploy vi\u001b[71G phone\"\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcost\u001b[9Galmost nothing extra o\u001b[32G the\u001b[37Gt\u001b[39Ganspor\u001b[47Gsi\u001b[50Ge — branch 1's design\u001b[72Galready\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsplit\u001b[9Gcontrol from data.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mEstate move = detach + attach\u001b[22m,\u001b[36Gnot\u001b[40Gcopy.\u001b[46GBecause\u001b[54Gthe\u001b[58Gsession\u001b[66Gis\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Breconstructable from connectome al\u001b[38Gne (the\u001b[46Gr\u001b[49Gon\u001b[52Gtruction rule), moving\u001b[75Gfrom\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bd\u001b[5Gvsta\u001b[10Gion to the Wind\u001b[26Gws box is: \u001b[38Gld\u001b[41Ga\u001b[43Gtachment ends, new device attaches,\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boutbox replays from \u001b[3mthat device's\u001b[37G\u001b[23mlast-seen cursor. Per-attachment cursor\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bno\u001b[6G per-session — that's the one schema d\u001b[45Gtail the estate move forces.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mQR ceremony\u001b[22m: the QR encod\u001b[31Gs a short-liv\u001b[45Gd boo\u001b[51Gstrap token + clyffy's\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bendpoint + key\u001b[18Gfingerprint. Phone scans → hits \u001b[51Ghe HTTP co\u001b[62Gtrol plane →\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1Brolls its own device keypair (branch 1's enrollment flow, unchanged) →\u001b[76Ggets\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Ba \u001b[38;5;153mdispatcher\u001b[39m attachment. Preflight = dry-run \u001b[49Geport over the control plane\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(\"this will run X against Y, estimate\u001b[41G Z\") →\u001b[48Gyou confirm\u001b[60G→ clyffy runs it,\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
