[353.552914, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G(read-only, reserved). A phone disp\u001b[39Gtch \u001b[44Gever\u001b[49Gneeds the QUIC\u001b[64Gfast\u001b[69Gpath; it\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bne\u001b[6Gds the HTTP/3 control\u001b[29Gla\u001b[34Gto \u001b[38Greflight and fire. So \"deploy vi\u001b[71G phone\"\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcost\u001b[9Galmost nothing extra o\u001b[32G the\u001b[37Gt\u001b[39Ganspor\u001b[47Gsi\u001b[50Ge — branch 1's design\u001b[72Galready\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsplit\u001b[9Gcontrol from data.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mEstate move = detach + attach\u001b[22m,\u001b[36Gnot\u001b[40Gcopy.\u001b[46GBecause\u001b[54Gthe\u001b[58Gsession\u001b[66Gis\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Breconstructable from connectome al\u001b[38Gne (the\u001b[46Gr\u001b[49Gon\u001b[52Gtruction rule), moving\u001b[75Gfrom\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bd\u001b[5Gvsta\u001b[10Gion to the Wind\u001b[26Gws box is: \u001b[38Gld\u001b[41Ga\u001b[43Gtachment ends, new device attaches,\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boutbox replays from \u001b[3mthat device's\u001b[37G\u001b[23mlast-seen cursor. Per-attachment cursor\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bno\u001b[6G per-session — that's the one schema d\u001b[45Gtail the estate move forces.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mQR ceremony\u001b[22m: the QR encod\u001b[31Gs a short-liv\u001b[45Gd boo\u001b[51Gstrap token + clyffy's\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bendpoint + key\u001b[18Gfingerprint. Phone scans → hits \u001b[51Ghe HTTP co\u001b[62Gtrol plane →\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1Brolls its own device keypair (branch 1's enrollment flow, unchanged) →\u001b[76Ggets\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Ba \u001b[38;5;153mdispatcher\u001b[39m attachment. Preflight = dry-run \u001b[49Geport over the control plane\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(\"this will run X against Y, estimate\u001b[41G Z\") →\u001b[48Gyou confirm\u001b[60G→ clyffy runs it,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsess\u001b[8Gon goes Adrift-w\u001b[25Gth-work, results\u001b[42Gland in the outbox for whatever\u001b[74Gdevice\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[354.023294, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Gsplit control from \u001b[23Gata.\u001b[28G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mEstate move = detach + attach\u001b[22m, not copy. Because the session is\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Breconstructable from\u001b[24Gconnectome alone (the reconstruction\u001b[61Grule), moving from\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdevs\u001b[8Gation to\u001b[17Gthe Windows\u001b[29Gbox\u001b[33Gis:\u001b[37Gold\u001b[41Gattachment\u001b[52Gends,\u001b[58Gnew\u001b[62Gdevice\u001b[69Gattaches,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Boutbox replays from \u001b[3mthat device's\u001b[23m last-seen cursor. P\u001b[57Gr-attachment\u001b[70Gcursors,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bnot per-session\u001b[19G— that's the one sch\u001b[40Gma d\u001b[45Gtail the es\u001b[57Gate\u001b[61Gmov\u001b[65G forces.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1mQR ceremony\u001b[22m: the QR encodes\u001b[33Ga sh\u001b[38Grt-lived boo\u001b[51Gstrap token + clyffy's\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bendp\u001b[8Gint + key\u001b[19Gingerprint. Phone\u001b[37Gscans → hits the HTTP control plane →\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Benrolls it\u001b[14G ow\u001b[19Gdevice keypair (branch 1's enrollment flow, unchang\u001b[71Gd)\u001b[74G→\u001b[76Ggets\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Ba\u001b[5G\u001b[38;5;153mdispatcher\u001b[39m at\u001b[19Gachment. Pr\u001b[31Gflight = dry-run report over the control plane\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(\"this will run X against Y, estimated Z\") → you confirm → clyffy runs it,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsession\u001b[11Ggoes Adrift-with-work,\u001b[34Gresults\u001b[42Gland in the outbox for w\u001b[68Gtever\u001b[74Gdevice\r\u001b[3C\u001b[1Bttaches next. That last\u001b[28Gpart \u001b[34Gs \u001b[37Ghe\u001b[40Gneut\u001b[45Gal-space m\u001b[56Gd\u001b[58Gl\u001b[60Gpaying off:\u001b[72Gthe phone\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdoesn't have to\u001b[19Gst\u001b[22Gy connected \u001b[35Go ke\u001b[40Gp\u001b[42Gthe\u001b[46Gdispat\u001b[53Gh running.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
