[355.908257, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3Gendpoint + key\u001b[18Gfingerprint. Phone scans → hits \u001b[51Ghe HTTP co\u001b[62Gtrol plane →\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1Brolls its own device keypair (branch 1's enrollment flow, unchanged) →\u001b[76Ggets\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Ba \u001b[38;5;153mdispatcher\u001b[39m attachment. Preflight = dry-run \u001b[49Geport over the control plane\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(\"this will run X against Y, estimate\u001b[41G Z\") →\u001b[48Gyou confirm\u001b[60G→ clyffy runs it,\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsess\u001b[8Gon goes Adrift-w\u001b[25Gth-work, results\u001b[42Gland in the outbox for whatever\u001b[74Gdevice\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Battaches n\u001b[14Gxt. Tha\u001b[22G last pa\u001b[31Gt is the neutral-spac\u001b[54Gmodel paying off: the phone\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdoesn't have to stay connected to k\u001b[39Gep the di\u001b[51Gtch running.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BSo:\u001b[7G\u001b[1mv1 = single-device sessions; the ledger is born multi-attach.\u001b[69G\u001b[22mDispatches\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Band\u001b[7Gestate moves are later ceremonies on an already-correct schema.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BTwo\u001b[7Gthings\u001b[14Gstill\u001b[20Gopen\u001b[25Gbefore\u001b[32Gthis\u001b[37Gbranch\u001b[44Gcan\u001b[48Gclose:\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B1.\u001b[6G\u001b[1mSession granularity\u001b[26G\u001b[22m—\u001b[28Gis\u001b[31Ga\u001b[33Gsession\u001b[41Ga\u001b[43GDevPulse\u001b[52G\u001b[3mworkspace\u001b[62G\u001b[23m(weeks-long),\u001b[76Ga\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[3mconversation/task\u001b[23m (hours-days), or a\u001b[41G\u001b[3mingestion job\u001b[23m? This sets outb\u001b[71Gx\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
