[455.278128, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mLocked in: \u001b[1mdestructive ops require a live primary attach, unless bypass is \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Barmed.\u001b[10G\u001b[22mThe\u001b[14Gway\u001b[18GI'd\u001b[22Gshape\u001b[28Gbypass\u001b[35Gso\u001b[38Git\u001b[41Gstays\u001b[47Ghonest:\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5GBypass\u001b[12Gis\u001b[15Ga\u001b[17G\u001b[1msession-scoped flag\u001b[22m,\u001b[38Garmed\u001b[44Gonly\u001b[49Gfrom\u001b[54Ga\u001b[56Glive\u001b[61Gprimary\u001b[69Gattach\r\u001b[1B \u001b[3G(arming is\u001b[14Ga deliberate act — a dispatcher/phone can't arm it, though it \u001b[3mcan\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[23mbenefit from it once \u001b[25Grmed).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5GArming,\u001b[13Gand\u001b[17G\u001b[1mevery destructive action executed under bypass while Adrift\u001b[22m,\u001b[78Gis\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Ba\u001b[5Ghash-chained ledger event — so the au\u001b[43Git trail shows exactly what r\u001b[73Gn\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bunwatched and under whose arming. Mirrors the \u001b[38;5;153m⏵⏵ bypass permissions\u001b[39m pat\u001b[75Gern\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Byou already l\u001b[17Gve in with Claude\u001b[35GCode:\u001b[41Gexplicit,\u001b[51Gvisible,\u001b[60Glogged.\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1BDefault\u001b[13Goff\u001b[17Gon every new session; survives reconnects (it's session state in\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bconnectome, not connectio\u001b[29G state); cleared\u001b[46Gon explicit\u001b[58Gdisarm or session\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bclose.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
