[456.11604, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H \u001b[3G- Bypass is a \u001b[1msession-scoped flag\u001b[22m, armed only from a live primary attach\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(arming is\u001b[14Ga deliberate act — a\u001b[35Gdispatcher/p\u001b[51G can't\u001b[58Garm\u001b[62Git,\u001b[66Gthough\u001b[73Git\u001b[76G\u001b[3mcan\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[23mbenefit\u001b[11Gfrom\u001b[16Git\u001b[19Gonce\u001b[24Garmed).\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1BArming, and\u001b[17G\u001b[1mevery de\u001b[26Gtructive action executed under bypass while Adrift\u001b[22m,\u001b[78Gis\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Ba hash-chaine\u001b[17G \u001b[19Gedger \u001b[26Gven\u001b[33Gso the audit trail\u001b[52Gshows\u001b[58Gexactly\u001b[66Gw\u001b[68Gat ran\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bunwatched and under whos\u001b[28G arming.\u001b[37GMirrors\u001b[45Gthe\u001b[49G\u001b[38;5;153m⏵⏵ bypass permissions\u001b[71G\u001b[39mpattern\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Byou already live in with Claude Code: explicit, visible, logged.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5GDefault off on ev\u001b[24Gy n\u001b[28Gw ses\u001b[34Gion; surv\u001b[44Gves reconnects (it's session state\u001b[79Gin\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bconne\u001b[9Gtome, not connection state); clea\u001b[43Ged on\u001b[49Gexplicit disarm or session\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bclose.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BThat resolves Adrift \u001b[25Gompletely: \u001b[3mnothing pauses, ever; destructive work queues\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bwaiting for a primary attach unless bypass says otherwise; the queue-vs-ran \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdistinction is visible in the ledger.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[23m\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
