[461.197955, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G\u001b[1mOne question left and this branch can close — session granularity.\u001b[70G\u001b[22mIs\u001b[73Ga\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsession:\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5G\u001b[1m(a) a DevPulse workspace\u001b[30G\u001b[22m—\u001b[32Gweeks-long,\u001b[44Gfew\u001b[48Gof\u001b[51Gthem,\u001b[57Goutbox\u001b[64Gretention\u001b[74Gis\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bcheap to reason about, \"my\u001b[30Gdevstation workspace\" ≈ one session;\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1m(b) a conversation/task\u001b[22m — hours-t\u001b[39G-days, m\u001b[48Gny per workspace, finer-grained\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bestate moves (move \u001b[3mthis task\u001b[23m to the laptop), but more ledger rows and a\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bworkspace-grouping\u001b[22Gconcept on top;\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1m(c) an ingestion job\u001b[22m — \u001b[29Go\u001b[31G fine,\u001b[38GI'd\u001b[42Gargue\u001b[48Gagainst:\u001b[57Gjobs\u001b[62Gshould\u001b[69Gbe\u001b[72G\u001b[3mwork \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bitems inside\u001b[23m a session, not sessions themselves, or the phone-dispatch story\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfragments.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BMy\u001b[6Grecommendation:\u001b[22G\u001b[1m(a) workspace-grained sessions, with jobs/conversations as \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bchild work-items\u001b[22m inside them. That keeps sessions rare and long-lived (matches\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"clyffy stays operat\u001b[24Gonal\" — the session\u001b[44Gba\u001b[47Gically never ends), mak\u001b[71Gs\u001b[73Gthe QR\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
