[462.558542, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G- \u001b[1m(b) a conversation/task\u001b[29G\u001b[22m—\u001b[31Ghours-to-days,\u001b[46Gmany\u001b[51Gper\u001b[55Gworkspace,\u001b[66Gfiner-grained\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bestate\u001b[10Gmoves\u001b[16G(move\u001b[22G\u001b[3mthis task\u001b[32G\u001b[23mto\u001b[35Gthe\u001b[39Glaptop),\u001b[48Gbut\u001b[52Gmore\u001b[57Gledger\u001b[64Grows\u001b[69Gand\u001b[73Ga\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bworkspace-grouping concept\u001b[30Gon top;\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- \u001b[1m(c) an ingestion job\u001b[26G\u001b[22m— too fine, I'd a\u001b[44Ggue against: job\u001b[61G should\u001b[69Gbe\u001b[72G\u001b[3mwork \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bitems inside\u001b[23m a session, not\u001b[31Gsessions themselves, o\u001b[55Gthe phon\u001b[64G-dispatch story\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bfragm\u001b[9Gnts.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BMy recommendation: \u001b[1m(a) workspace-grained sessions, with jobs/conversations as \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bchild work-items\u001b[22m inside\u001b[27Gthem. That keeps \u001b[46Gssions \u001b[54Gare and long-lived (matches\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"clyffy \u001b[12Gtays\u001b[17Goperational\"\u001b[30G—\u001b[32Gthe\u001b[36Gsession\u001b[44Gbasically\u001b[54Gnever\u001b[60Gends),\u001b[67Gmakes\u001b[73Gthe\u001b[77GQR\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdispatch\u001b[12Ga\u001b[14Gwork-item\u001b[24Gceremony\u001b[33Grather\u001b[40Gthan\u001b[45Ga\u001b[47Gsession\u001b[55Gceremony,\u001b[65Gand\u001b[69Gleaves\u001b[76Groom\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bto\u001b[6Gpromot\u001b[13G a work-item to its own session later if you ever need per-task\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bestate moves. Which way\u001b[27Gdo you w\u001b[36Gnt it?\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;174m✢\u001b[3GFlu\u001b[38;5;216mtte\u001b[38;5;174mring… \u001b[38;5;246m(21s · ↓\u001b[24G786 tokens)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
