[501.230696, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[25C\u001b[7B\u001b[1mworkspace-grained sessions, with jobs/conversations as \r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bchild work-items\u001b[22m inside them. That keeps sessions rare and long-lived (matches\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"clyffy stays operational\" — the session basically never ends), makes the QR\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bdispatch a work-item ceremony rather than a session ceremony, and leaves room\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bto promote a work-item to its own session later if you ever need per-task\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bestate moves. \u001b[23;1H\u001b[19;4H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
